<h3><U>About Me:</U></h3>
<p><font size="+1">So who am I ?<br/>Let's start of with the basics, my name is Nitin Devin Arun.<br/>
    Currently aged 18 years old and born on 23rd December 2000
    <br/>I was born and raised in Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia.
    <br/>For those of you that don't know where that is, the image above shows it.
    <br/>After much of my schooling life in KL, I have now moved to Aberystwyth for University.
<h3><u>Passions & Hobbies:</u></h3>
    <p>To list a couple of my hobbies & passions, I am heavily invested into cars; more specifically Performance cars.
    <br/>On top of that, I am also a DJ and have been posting mixes & content on Instagram.
    <br/> Lastly, I have an extensive passion for diving and Underwater Videography. I post all of my videos on FaceBook.
    <br/> Find my videos for my DJing @nitinarun on Instagram & my diving videos @Nitin Arun on FaceBook.
    <br/>In Conclusion, I am a pretty average guy with a semi-interesting life.</font></p>

